    </p>

    <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-black">Current Role</h2>

    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      As Director of Product Management at Cockroach Labs, I own CockroachDB's integration with the broader application ecosystem, including observability, disaster recovery, change data capture (CDC), streaming, and migration workflows across hybrid and cloud environments. I also lead our pricing and packaging strategy, aligning product value with business outcomes through a data-driven, iterative approach to product-market-price fit.
