    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-lg">
      <li>Enterprise B2B user journeys across SaaS, open-core, and enterprise licensing models</li>
      <li>Go-to-Market (GTM): product-led growth (PLG/PLS), sales-assisted motions, and field sales enablement</li>
      <li>Distributed infrastructure and databases, including CSP integrations (AWS, GCP, Azure)</li>
      <li>AI/ML infrastructure: LLMs, RAG architectures, vector databases, and production deployment</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-black">Technical & Strategic Skills</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-lg">
      <li>People leadership: hiring, coaching, and performance management across functions</li>
      <li>Product strategy: investment planning, ROI analysis, budgeting, and analytics</li>
      <li>End-to-end product development: from discovery and design to docs and delivery</li>
      <li>Analytics & Financial Modeling: SQL/Looker fluency, revenue forecasting, NRR/NDR, gross margin optimization, LTV:CAC, Rule of 40</li>
      <li>Pricing & monetization: strategy informed by data science, customer research, and business modeling</li>
      <li>Technical: Python, SQL, LLMs (GPT-4, Claude, Vertex AI), RAG, Vector Databases, Prompt Engineering</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-black">Let's Connect</h2>

    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Always up to explore the intersection of AI and infrastructure, or debate the perfect burger. Reach out on <a href="https://twitter.com/iamandywoods" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-black underline hover:opacity-70">X</a> or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewscottwoods/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-black underline hover:opacity-70">LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
